; OpenClaw One-Click Installer - NSIS Custom Script
; ClawJacked Shield: Security-hardened NSIS installer customizations

; This file is included by electron-builder during the NSIS packaging step.
; It can be used to add custom NSIS installer logic.

; No custom macros required for the base build.
; The ClawJacked Shield security hardening is handled by install.ps1 at runtime.
